QuestData.Title: Stag Soul
QuestData.Description: <The Stag Soul is noble and mighty. The shape of the stag will be yours to call upon.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Stag Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the Stag Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, the stag. This shape is now yours to call upon.
